high_descs: Turn around and step forward to face the knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the right side of the sink.
Cut the potato in the right side of the sink.
Place the knife in the sink with the potato.
Pick up a slice of the potato in the sink.
Take a step back and look up to face the microwave.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the fridge.
Place the potato slice in the fridge beside the tomato.
anns.task_desc: To heat a potato slice as well as place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the counter to the right of the sink.
Take the large knife behind the apple from the counter.
Go in front of the sink on the left.
Cut the potato in the sink into slices.
Put the knife in the sink.
Take a slice of potato from the sink.
Go to the left a step, look above the sink at the microwave.
Cook the potato in the microwave. Take the potato from the microwave.
Turn right, go forward, stop at the wooden cabinets to the left, turn right to the fridge, go forward to the fridge.
Put the potato in front of the apple in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato in a fridge.

high_descs: Go to the counter right of the sink
Pick up a knife from the counter
Go to the sink
Cut the potato in the sink
Place the knife in the sink
Pick up a potato slice from the sink
Go to the microwave
Heat the potato slice in the microwave
Go to the fridge
Place the potato slice in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato slice in a fridge
